name: Business Actor
description: Represents an organizational entity involved in business processes

name: Business Role
description: Represents a responsibility assigned to an actor

name: Business Process
description: Describes a sequence of business behaviors

name: Application Service
description: Exposes application behavior to its environment

name: Artifact
description: A physical piece of data used or produced in processes

name: Capability
description: An ability that an active structure element possesses

name: Course of Action
description: An approach or plan for achieving a goal

name: Value Stream
description: A sequence of activities creating customer value
